       Chapman, 22-Oct-2007.) $)
    ref $p |- Re : CC --> RR $=
      ( vx cv ccj cfv caddc co c2 cdiv cr wcel cc wral reval recl eqeltrrd rgen
      cre wf df-re fmpt mpbi ) ABZUBCDEFGHFZIJZAKLKIQRUDAKUBKJUBQDUCIUBMUBNOPAK
