    $( Domain and codomain of the imaginary part function.  (Contributed by
       Paul Chapman, 22-Oct-2007.) $)
    imf $p |- Im : CC --> RR $=
      ( vx cv ci cdiv co cre cfv cr wcel cc wral imval imcl eqeltrrd rgen df-im
